{"tid":1827682,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"【急召救亡】《雷神3》導演泰格 獲斟執導新《星球大戰》","createTime":"2020-01-17T06:48:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-07T17:26:52.000Z","uid":130626,"like":12,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":53,"replies":[{"pid":"aa80478a6d1a2b8c83a5bc38a6669edf466a2842","tid":1827682,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T06:48:28.000Z","msg":"《雷神奇俠3：諸神黃昏》（Thor：Ragnarok）導演泰格韋替替（Taika Waititi），最近之新作《陽光兔仔兵》 （Jojo Rabbit）獲不少奧斯卡提名，而最近就有消息指，迪士尼希望邀請他執導新的《星球大戰》（Star Wars）電影，為系列救亡。<br />\n<br />\n其實《星球大戰》除了正傳之外，外傳系列都口碑麻麻，而雖然迪士尼發佈過初步計劃，指 2022、2024與2026年都有《星戰》戲上映，但到現在仍然未有進一步消息。其實上年電影公司曾公佈《權力遊戲》（Game of Thrones）創作人David Benioff與Dan Weiss會製作新3步曲，但到上年10月又被炒魷，相信泰格韋替替之加入，應該會為《星戰》帶來新鮮感。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200117/large/1579237765_b0fe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200117%2Flarge%2F1579237765_b0fe.jpg&h=8c9d9536&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200117/HNCUXNX7MR37JKDMK42XERM56U/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200117%2FHNCUXNX7MR37JKDMK42XERM56U%2F&d=yrakYkBpMe8E3VCHF0kcyuSCO5RJLUOM1IbOSdmZk8c%3D&h=0a21fb32\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200117%2FHNCUXNX7MR37JKDMK42XERM56U%2F&h=3020c2cd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200117/HNCUXNX7MR37JKDMK42XERM56U/</a>"},{"pid":"e633ed4fff1d59d9853e5d0fc43f3da2ff529b0e","tid":1827682,"uid":37876,"like":41,"dislike":2,"score":39,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T06:50:58.000Z","msg":"然後佢又會演埋一份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b34bde03a7111df090eccec1ea8977562a5b649","tid":1827682,"uid":170244,"like":28,"dislike":2,"score":26,"quote":{"pid":"e633ed4fff1d59d9853e5d0fc43f3da2ff5